        <h1>What is E-procurement System</h1>
        <p>
          <h4>  Welcome to eProcurement System </h4>
</p>
<p>The eProcurement System of India enables the Tenderers to download the Tender Schedule free of cost and then submit the bids online through this portal
        </p>
