            This website as a connection link to reduce the communication time to the minimum for better coordination among Suppliers/ Contractors, Clients and EIL.This  Portal provides online facility to the Suppliers& Contractors, Clients and EIL users to  view & download  all the Press & Limited Tenders / Enquiries, due for submission of bids.  We welcome your * feedback / suggestions for improving this website  as we want to continue to streamline the website based on your feedback.
